248
00:13:59,271 --> 00:14:01,569
And I haven't forgotten
our new believers.

249
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:04,074
About this time on Sundays,
I like to remember-

250
00:14:04,143 --> 00:14:09,012
GATES: But WDIA's contribution
