251
00:14:09,081 --> 00:14:12,847
Before long, white kids
began tuning in as well,

252
00:14:12,918 --> 00:14:15,785
giving the station
an interracial audience

253
00:14:15,855 --> 00:14:18,153
in the Jim Crow South.

254
00:14:18,224 --> 00:14:21,921
So, in spite of
the fact that Memphis
is strictly segregated,

255
00:14:21,994 --> 00:14:24,224
white people are
listening to black music

256
00:14:24,296 --> 00:14:27,322
being played and
narrated by black DJs.

257
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:29,390
Sure. What I think
is really fascinating

258
00:14:29,468 --> 00:14:31,163
