00:15:15,514 --> 00:15:18,039
GATES: 5 years later,
Dorothy Dandridge

275
00:15:18,117 --> 00:15:20,051
became the first
African-American

276
00:15:20,119 --> 00:15:23,577
nominated for an Academy Award
