bring to your side

396
00:22:32,451 --> 00:22:36,547
forces governmental,
religious, international

397
00:22:36,621 --> 00:22:42,821
is by allowing yourself to be
so maltreated visibly

398
00:22:42,894 --> 00:22:46,830
that your assailant
loses credibility.

399
00:22:51,603 --> 00:22:55,937
GATES: The clash
between peaceful protests
and violent resistance

400
00:22:56,007 --> 00:22:58,840
would produce images
that caused the country

401
00:22:58,910 --> 00:23:01,105
to sit up and take notice.

402
00:23:04,249 --> 00:23:09,312
In New Orleans, on the morning
of November 14, 1960,

403
00:23:09,388 --> 00:23:12,880
federal marshals escorted
a 6-year-old gin

404
00:23:12,958 --> 00:23:17,952
named Ruby Bridges to the local,
all-white elementary school.

405
00:23:19,097 --> 00:23:22,965
WOMAN: I remember
turning onto the street.

406
00:23:23,034 --> 00:23:26,060
I saw barricades
and police officers

407
00:23:26,138 --> 00:23:29,198
and just
people everywhere.

408
00:23:29,274 --> 00:23:31,071
When I saw all of that,

409
00:23:31,143 --> 00:23:33,270
I immediately thought
that it was Mardi Gras.

410
00:23:33,345 --> 00:23:35,074
Ha ha!
I had no idea

411
00:23:35,147 --> 00:23:38,173
that they were here
to keep me out of
the school.

412
00:23:38,250 --> 00:23:40,241
Ruby, were you scared?
I would have
been terrified.

413
00:23:40,318 --> 00:23:42,411
I wasn't, actually,
because, you know,

414
00:23:42,487 --> 00:23:44,455
it was very hard
for parents, I think,

415
00:23:44,523 --> 00:23:46,388
to explain
to a 6-year-old

416
00:23:46,458 --> 00:23:48,016
what was
actually happening.

417
00:23:48,093 --> 00:23:50,618
They didn't say,
"it's a white school.
You're making history"?

418
00:23:50,695 --> 00:23:53,061
I remember them saying
"Ruby, you're gonna go to

419
00:23:53,131 --> 00:23:55,099
a new school today,
and you better behave."

420
00:23:56,802 --> 00:23:59,669
GATES: But Ruby
was making history.

421
00:23:59,738 --> 00:24:03,765
6 years earlier,
after decades of struggle,

422
00:24:03,842 --> 00:24:07,676
the NAACP had won
a major legal victory-

423
00:24:07,746 --> 00:24:10,271
Brown v. Board of Education,

424
00:24:10,348 --> 00:24:12,543
in which the Supreme
Court declared

425
00:24:12,617 --> 00:24:15,518
that the doctrine of
separate but equal schools

426
00:24:15,587 --> 00:24:18,181
was unconstitutional.

427
00:24:18,256 --> 00:24:23,353
But in many places, that triumph
did not translate into change.

428
00:24:24,796 --> 00:24:27,731
For years after Brown,
much of the South

429
00:24:27,799 --> 00:24:29,494
simply refused to integrate.

430
00:24:31,136 --> 00:24:35,266
Now Ruby would be one of
6 New Orleans children

431
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:41,279
chosen to desegregate several
all-white elementary schools.

432
00:24:41,346 --> 00:24:43,075
BRIDGES: They were
screaming and shouting

433
00:24:43,148 --> 00:24:46,584
and chanting "2, 4, 6, 8,
we don't want to integrate."

434
00:24:46,651 --> 00:24:50,109
[Crowd chanting] 2, 4, 6, 8,
we don't want to integrate.

435
00:24:50,188 --> 00:24:51,655
2, 4, 6, 8...

436
00:24:51,723 --> 00:24:53,520
MAN ON TV: The mothers of
downtown New Orleans

437
00:24:53,592 --> 00:24:55,787
screaming at a Negro child
as she entered

438
00:24:55,861 --> 00:24:58,091
the William Frantz
Elementary School,

439
00:24:58,163 --> 00:25:00,597
first in the city
to be integrated.

440
00:25:00,665 --> 00:25:01,893
BRIDGES: Once I got
into the school,

441
00:25:01,967 --> 00:25:05,494
all of these people here
rushed inside of
the building.

442
00:25:05,570 --> 00:25:09,062
[indistinct chanting]

443
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:11,335
BRIDGES: They were
taking out their children.

444
00:25:11,409 --> 00:25:14,401
Over 500 kids walked out
of school that day.

445
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:20,909
MAN: What is your reaction
to the court's decision

446
00:25:20,986 --> 00:25:22,419
continuing integration?

447
00:25:22,487 --> 00:25:24,648
We don't want
the niggers going
in that school.

448
00:25:24,723 --> 00:25:26,714
Well...
This is
a white school.

449
00:25:29,928 --> 00:25:34,456
BRIDGES: They didn't
see a child.

450
00:25:34,533 --> 00:25:37,730
They saw change,

451
00:25:37,802 --> 00:25:41,670
and what they thought was
being taken from them.

452
00:25:42,874 --> 00:25:44,637
They never saw a child.

453
00:25:44,709 --> 00:25:48,167
WOMEN: <i>°</i> if you believe <i>°</i>

454
00:25:50,782 --> 00:25:55,014
<i>°</i> The faith you lost
