455
00:25:59,457 --> 00:26:03,860
<i>°</i> Will return upon your shore <i>°</i>

456
00:26:07,132 --> 00:26:09,657
GATES: The image of
a 6-year-old child

457
00:26:09,734 --> 00:26:11,702
heckled by an angry mob

458
00:26:11,770 --> 00:26:15,331
became a powerful icon
for the young movement.

459
00:26:15,407 --> 00:26:19,138
Ruby's example
