474
00:27:01,820 --> 00:27:03,583
We saw through that.

475
00:27:03,655 --> 00:27:05,384
And now here was
our moment

476
00:27:05,457 --> 00:27:08,949
to challenge our
nation to recognize

477
00:27:09,027 --> 00:27:10,756
that we are
hypocrites,

478
00:27:10,829 --> 00:27:12,160
and this is
our opportunity

479
00:27:12,230 --> 00:27:13,629
to try to make
this right.

480
00:27:13,698 --> 00:27:16,826
[Crowd chanting] ...want to
integrate, 2, 4, 6, 8...

481
00:27:16,901 --> 00:27:19,802
GATES: Charlayne Hunter
and Hamilton Holmes

482
00:27:19,871 --> 00:27:24,274
