00:49:19,856 --> 00:49:21,824
GATES: Carmichael
and the militant activists-

892
00:49:21,892 --> 00:49:26,192
they're thinking that civil
rights has not gone far enough.

893
00:49:26,263 --> 00:49:29,130
They want liberation
and freedom now.

894
00:49:29,199 --> 00:49:31,030
MAN: <i>°</i> Freedom's
